TY  - JOUR
T1  - Confidence Intervals for Diffusion Index Forecasts and Inference for Factor-Augmented Regressions
AU  - Bai, Jushan
AU  - Ng, Serena
Y1  - 2006/07/01
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/07/01
